This file attempts to describe the Rule system used in PLN.

== Overview ==

Rules in PLN describe the process of creating new atoms in the AtomSpace. What
are the required atoms to create the new atom, and their relationship. It also
controls computation of the TruthValue for the new atom by calling the
appropriate formula (see ../formulas/README) and checking the validity of the
arguments to the rule.

== List of Rules ==

The rules have been divided up into different groupings

-- and Rules --

AND2ORRule
ANDBreakdownRule
ANDPartitionRule
ANDRuleArityFree
ANDRule
ANDRuleSimple
ANDSubstRule

-- or Rules --

OR2ANDRule
ORPartitionRule
ORRule

-- not Rules --

NotEliminationRule.h
NotEvaluatorRule.h

-- inference Rules --

DeductionRule.h
HypothesisRule.h
InversionRule.h
QuantifierRule.h
RevisionRule.h

-- implication Rules --

ImplicationBreakdownRule.h
